OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain expected for much of the evening
OL,7,Fas a band of rain moves southeastwards
OL,8,Facross the region. Becoming mostly dry
OL,9,Flater in the night, with a few clear
OL,10,Fspells developing towards dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAfter a cool start, it will
OL,13,Fbe a dry day, with variable amounts of
OL,14,Fcloud and some bright or sunny spells.
OL,15,FFeeling cooler compared to previous
OL,16,Fdays. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
